<p>The compare view gives a preview of selected fonts (useful for comparison of e.g. a number of fonts for a project).</p>

<p>Add fonts to your comparison by selecting fonts from the main font list and pressing the + button. </p>

<p>Change background and foreground colors with the color pickers in the upper-right corner. </p>
